    "51": {
      "content": "### ArgoCD Sync Pulse\n\nThis dashboard provides a comprehensive view of the status of ArgoCD notifications related to the deployment of new applications. It is designed to help platform engineers and DevOps teams monitor and manage their deployment processes effectively.",
      "title": "",
      "type": "markdown"
    },
